INSERT INTO
    ab_user
(
    ID,
    FIRST_NAME,
    LAST_NAME,
    USERNAME,
    PASSWORD,
    ACTIVE,
    EMAIL,
    LAST_LOGIN,
    LOGIN_COUNT,
    FAIL_LOGIN_COUNT,
    CREATED_ON,
    CHANGED_ON,
    CREATED_BY_FK,
    CHANGED_BY_FK
)
VALUES (
    :ID,
    :FIRST_NAME,
    :LAST_NAME,
    :USERNAME,
    :PASSWORD,
    :ACTIVE,
    :EMAIL,
    :LAST_LOGIN,
    :LOGIN_COUNT,
    :FAIL_LOGIN_COUNT,
    :CREATED_ON,
    :CHANGED_ON,
    :CREATED_BY_FK,
    :CHANGED_BY_FK
)

DELETE FROM
    ab_user
WHERE
    ID = :ID
    AND FIRST_NAME = :FIRST_NAME
    AND LAST_NAME = :LAST_NAME
    AND USERNAME = :USERNAME
    AND EMAIL = :EMAIL

UPDATE
    ab_user
SET
    PASSWORD = :PASSWORD,
    ACTIVE = :ACTIVE,
    LAST_LOGIN = :LAST_LOGIN,
    LOGIN_COUNT = :LOGIN_COUNT,
    FAIL_LOGIN_COUNT = :FAIL_LOGIN_COUNT,
    CREATED_ON = :CREATED_ON,
    CHANGED_ON = :CHANGED_ON,
    CREATED_BY_FK = :CREATED_BY_FK,
    CHANGED_BY_FK = :CHANGED_BY_FK
WHERE
    ID = :ID
    AND FIRST_NAME = :FIRST_NAME
    AND LAST_NAME = :LAST_NAME
    AND USERNAME = :USERNAME
    AND EMAIL = :EMAIL

SELECT 
    ID,
    FIRST_NAME,
    LAST_NAME,
    USERNAME,
    PASSWORD,
    CASE WHEN ACTIVE = 'true' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END ACTIVE,
    EMAIL,
    LAST_LOGIN,
    LOGIN_COUNT,
    FAIL_LOGIN_COUNT,
    CREATED_ON,
    CHANGED_ON,
    CREATED_BY_FK,
    CHANGED_BY_FK 
FROM 
  ab_user

INSERT INTO
    variable
(
    ID,
    KEY,
    VAL,
    DESCRIPTION,
    IS_ENCRYPTED
)
VALUES (
    :ID,
    :KEY,
    :VAL,
    :DESCRIPTION,
    :IS_ENCRYPTED
)

SELECT 
    ID,
    KEY,
    VAL,
    DESCRIPTION,
    IS_ENCRYPTED 
FROM 
  variable

UPDATE
    variable
SET
    KEY = :KEY,
    VAL = :VAL,
    DESCRIPTION = :DESCRIPTION,
    IS_ENCRYPTED = :IS_ENCRYPTED
WHERE
    ID = :ID

INSERT INTO
    connection
(
    ID,
    CONN_ID,
    CONN_TYPE,
    DESCRIPTION,
    HOST,
    SCHEMA,
    LOGIN,
    PASSWORD,
    PORT,
    IS_ENCRYPTED,
    IS_EXTRA_ENCRYPTED,
    EXTRA
)
VALUES (
    :ID,
    :CONN_ID,
    :CONN_TYPE,
    :DESCRIPTION,
    :HOST,
    :SCHEMA,
    :LOGIN,
    :PASSWORD,
    :PORT,
    :IS_ENCRYPTED,
    :IS_EXTRA_ENCRYPTED,
    :EXTRA
)

DELETE FROM
    connection
WHERE
    ID = :ID
    AND CONN_ID = :CONN_ID
    AND CONN_TYPE = :CONN_TYPE

SELECT 
    ID,
    CONN_ID,
    CONN_TYPE,
    DESCRIPTION,
    HOST,
    SCHEMA,
    LOGIN,
    PASSWORD,
    PORT,
    IS_ENCRYPTED,
    IS_EXTRA_ENCRYPTED,
    EXTRA 
FROM 
  connection

UPDATE
    connection
SET
    DESCRIPTION = :DESCRIPTION,
    HOST = :HOST,
    SCHEMA = :SCHEMA,
    LOGIN = :LOGIN,
    PASSWORD = :PASSWORD,
    PORT = :PORT,
    IS_ENCRYPTED = :IS_ENCRYPTED,
    IS_EXTRA_ENCRYPTED = :IS_EXTRA_ENCRYPTED,
    EXTRA = :EXTRA
WHERE
    ID = :ID
    AND CONN_ID = :CONN_ID
    AND CONN_TYPE = :CONN_TYPE

INSERT INTO
    dag
(
    DAG_ID,
    ROOT_DAG_ID,
    IS_PAUSED,
    IS_SUBDAG,
    IS_ACTIVE,
    LAST_PARSED_TIME,
    LAST_PICKLED,
    LAST_EXPIRED,
    SCHEDULER_LOCK,
    PICKLE_ID,
    FILELOC,
    PROCESSOR_SUBDIR,
    OWNERS,
    DAG_DISPLAY_NAME,
    DESCRIPTION,
    DEFAULT_VIEW,
    SCHEDULE_INTERVAL,
    TIMETABLE_DESCRIPTION,
    DATASET_EXPRESSION,
    MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS,
    MAX_ACTIVE_RUNS,
    MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS,
    HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS,
    HAS_IMPORT_ERRORS,
    NEXT_DAGRUN,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_START,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_END,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_CREATE_AFTER
)
VALUES (
    :DAG_ID,
    :ROOT_DAG_ID,
    :IS_PAUSED,
    :IS_SUBDAG,
    :IS_ACTIVE,
    :LAST_PARSED_TIME,
    :LAST_PICKLED,
    :LAST_EXPIRED,
    :SCHEDULER_LOCK,
    :PICKLE_ID,
    :FILELOC,
    :PROCESSOR_SUBDIR,
    :OWNERS,
    :DAG_DISPLAY_NAME,
    :DESCRIPTION,
    :DEFAULT_VIEW,
    :SCHEDULE_INTERVAL,
    :TIMETABLE_DESCRIPTION,
    :DATASET_EXPRESSION,
    :MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS,
    :MAX_ACTIVE_RUNS,
    :MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS,
    :HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS,
    :HAS_IMPORT_ERRORS,
    :NEXT_DAGRUN,
    :NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_START,
    :NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_END,
    :NEXT_DAGRUN_CREATE_AFTER
)

DELETE FROM
    dag
WHERE
    DAG_ID = :DAG_ID
    AND MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS = :MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS
    AND MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS = :MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS
    AND HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS = :HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS

UPDATE
    dag
SET
    ROOT_DAG_ID = :ROOT_DAG_ID,
    IS_PAUSED = :IS_PAUSED,
    IS_SUBDAG = :IS_SUBDAG,
    IS_ACTIVE = :IS_ACTIVE,
    LAST_PARSED_TIME = :LAST_PARSED_TIME,
    LAST_PICKLED = :LAST_PICKLED,
    LAST_EXPIRED = :LAST_EXPIRED,
    SCHEDULER_LOCK = :SCHEDULER_LOCK,
    PICKLE_ID = :PICKLE_ID,
    FILELOC = :FILELOC,
    PROCESSOR_SUBDIR = :PROCESSOR_SUBDIR,
    OWNERS = :OWNERS,
    DAG_DISPLAY_NAME = :DAG_DISPLAY_NAME,
    DESCRIPTION = :DESCRIPTION,
    DEFAULT_VIEW = :DEFAULT_VIEW,
    SCHEDULE_INTERVAL = :SCHEDULE_INTERVAL,
    TIMETABLE_DESCRIPTION = :TIMETABLE_DESCRIPTION,
    DATASET_EXPRESSION = :DATASET_EXPRESSION,
    MAX_ACTIVE_RUNS = :MAX_ACTIVE_RUNS,
    HAS_IMPORT_ERRORS = :HAS_IMPORT_ERRORS,
    NEXT_DAGRUN = :NEXT_DAGRUN,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_START = :NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_START,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_END = :NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_END,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_CREATE_AFTER = :NEXT_DAGRUN_CREATE_AFTER
WHERE
    DAG_ID = :DAG_ID
    AND MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS = :MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS
    AND MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS = :MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS
    AND HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS = :HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS

SELECT 
    DAG.DAG_ID DAG_ID,
    dag_tag.NAME DAG_TAG,
    ROOT_DAG_ID,
    CASE WHEN IS_PAUSED = 'true' THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END IS_PAUSED,
    IS_SUBDAG,
    IS_ACTIVE,
    LAST_PARSED_TIME,
    LAST_PICKLED,
    LAST_EXPIRED,
    SCHEDULER_LOCK,
    PICKLE_ID,
    FILELOC,
    PROCESSOR_SUBDIR,
    OWNERS,
    DAG_DISPLAY_NAME,
    DESCRIPTION,
    DEFAULT_VIEW,
    SCHEDULE_INTERVAL,
    TIMETABLE_DESCRIPTION,
    DATASET_EXPRESSION,
    MAX_ACTIVE_TASKS,
    MAX_ACTIVE_RUNS,
    MAX_CONSECUTIVE_FAILED_DAG_RUNS,
    HAS_TASK_CONCURRENCY_LIMITS,
    HAS_IMPORT_ERRORS,
    NEXT_DAGRUN,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_START,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_DATA_INTERVAL_END,
    NEXT_DAGRUN_CREATE_AFTER 
FROM 
  dag
LEFT JOIN
  dag_tag
  ON dag_tag.dag_id = dag.dag_id
